      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "sea salt",
      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "Roll out the shortcrust pastry and place it in a tart pan.",
    "In a blender, blend the dates, smoked almond butter, brown sugar, lemon juice, water, vanilla extract, and sea salt until smooth.",
    "Pour the date mixture into the pastry shell.",
    "Bake the tart for 35 minutes or until the crust is golden brown.",
    "Let the tart cool completely before serving.",
    "Slice the tart into 8 pieces and serve.",
    "Garnish with additional smoked almond butter and dates if desired."
  ],
